OL,3,CPensioner tried to smuggle cocaine
OL,4,Cinto the UK hidden in mobility scooter
OL,6,FA pensioner who tried to smuggle
OL,7,Fcocaine worth more than #600,000 into
OL,8,Fthe UK hidden in his mobility scooter
OL,9,Fhas been jailed.
OL,11,FNational Crime Agency (NCA) officers
OL,12,Fbegan investigating 71-year-old Ronald
OL,13,FLord, from Montreal in Canada, after
OL,14,Fhe was stopped at Gatwick Airport on 7
OL,15,FFebruary 2025.
OL,17,FHe claimed he had been on a seven-day
OL,18,Fholiday to Barbados and was also
OL,19,Fcoming to the UK to sightsee.
