OL,3,CPensioner tried to smuggle cocaine
OL,4,Cinto the UK hidden in mobility scooter
OL,6,FAn x-ray of his scooter found eight
OL,7,Fkilos of the drug hidden in a void in
OL,8,Fthe seat back panel.
OL,10,FNCA experts valued the haul at around
OL,11,F#640,000, at street-level prices.
OL,13,FLord told NCA investigators that he
OL,14,Fdidn't know how it had got in there
OL,15,Fand denied any knowledge.
OL,17,FHowever, following a search a screw
OL,18,Ffrom the panel was found in his pocket.
