OL,3,CPensioner tried to smuggle cocaine
OL,4,Cinto the UK hidden in mobility scooter
OL,6,FInvestigators also found he had lied
OL,7,Fabout his time in Barbados, spending
OL,8,Fonly three days there before
OL,9,Ftravelling to the UK.
OL,11,FLord admitted class A drug smuggling
OL,12,Fcharges during a hearing at Croydon
OL,13,FCrown Court on 5 August.
OL,15,FA judge at the same court sentenced
OL,16,Fhim to six years in prison, on Friday
OL,17,F5 September.
