OL,3,CPensioner tried to smuggle cocaine
OL,4,Cinto the UK hidden in mobility scooter
OL,6,FNCA Senior Investigating Officer,
OL,7,FRichard Wickham, said: "Organised
OL,8,Fcrime groups need smugglers like Lord
OL,9,Fto bring class A drugs into the UK,
OL,10,Fwhere they are sold for huge profit by
OL,11,Fgangs who deal in violence and
OL,12,Fexploitation.
OL,14,F"He obviously thought that because he
OL,15,Fwas a pensioner he would be less of a
OL,16,Ftarget for law enforcement.
OL,18,F"He was wrong, and I hope this case
OL,19,Fsends out a message to anyone who
OL,20,Fwould consider doing the same.
